"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"In Midtown Manhattan, many streets were closed because a lot of fans gathered outside an arena for a big celebration.\",            \"english_title\": \"Streets Closed for Celebration\",            \"translated_version\": \"En Midtown Manhattan, muchas calles estaban cerradas porque muchos fans se juntaron afuera de una arena para una gran celebraci\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Calles Cerradas por Celebraci\u00f3n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"More than 165 million people are facing very hot and humid weather, with temperatures expected to stay around 38C (100F) for several days.\",            \"english_title\": \"Heatwave Affects Millions\",            \"translated_version\": \"M\u00e1s de 165 millones de personas est\u00e1n enfrentando clima muy caliente y h\u00famedo, con temperaturas que se esperan que queden alrededor de 38C (100F) por varios d\u00edas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ola de Calor Afecta a Millones\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Pope honored migrants who died at sea by visiting a cemetery on the Italian island of Lampedusa.\",            \"english_title\": \"Pope Honors Migrants\",            \"translated_version\": \"El Papa honr\u00f3 a los migrantes que murieron en el mar visitando un cementerio en la isla italiana de Lampedusa.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Papa Honra a Migrantes\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The daughter of former president Alberto Fujimori was declared the winner of a close election almost a month after the voting happened.\",            \"english_title\": \"Fujimori's Daughter Wins Election\",            \"translated_version\": \"La hija del ex presidente Alberto Fujimori fue declarada ganadora de una elecci\u00f3n cerrada casi un mes despu\u00e9s de que ocurri\u00f3 la votaci\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Hija de Fujimori Gana Elecci\u00f3n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Officials think the suspect in an attack might not have acted alone and spent days planning the attack.\",            \"english_title\": \"Attack Suspect Investigation\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los oficiales piensan que el sospechoso de un ataque podr\u00eda no haber actuado solo y pas\u00f3 d\u00edas planeando el ataque.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Investigaci\u00f3n de Sospechoso de Ataque\"        }    ]}"